name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
The mother was scolded by the police at the police station because she did not do nucleic acid test in time due to illness. After her son interrupted, he was dragged into the women's restroom by the police and beaten.
The latest development of the case: The three police officers involved in the case were tried publicly. In court, the three people repeatedly testified and shirked each other. The prosecutor: It is recommended that the three be sentenced to 9 months in prison and suspended sentences.
Before the trial, Mr. Sun obtained 188,000 yuan in compensation from the defendant through civil litigation. "This part of the compensation is based on facts, but I can't ask me to issue a letter of understanding and let them go to work normally as if nothing happened. I think they should be punished for their actions."

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
Recently, a TCM expert said that many people say that Western medicine is mixed into Chinese medicine. In fact, Oseltamivir is also mixed with Chinese medicine star anise. It’s just that the West wants to save face, so they write shikimic acid in the ingredients.
A doctoral student in medicine at Southeast University said: Oseltamivir and shikimic acid are not the same thing at all. Shikimic acid is at most an intermediate in its synthesis path, and shikimic acid is not only found in star anise. https://pbs.twimg.com/ext_tw_video_thumb/1883914703384276992/pu/img/bmpExC1bkNuJBeHV.jpg

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
Recently, Shi Jianjian, the last village bank depositor who was detained in Zhengzhou, Henan Province for rights protection on New Year's Eve last year, finally returned home to reunite with his family.
Because he never admitted his guilt, he was secretly sentenced by the Qinyang Municipal People's Court of Henan Province on January 23, 2025, and was sentenced to one year and two months in prison and suspended for one year and six months for the crime of provoking disturbances.
Today, Shi Jianjian wrote a letter of thanks to Lou Yangsheng, former secretary of the Henan Provincial Party Committee, and relevant departments of the Henan Provincial Government, thanking them for successfully turning an innocent depositor into a criminal on trumped-up charges. Thank them for turning him from a high-spirited middle-aged man into a skinny old man...

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
On January 28, the Democratic Republic of the Congo. The embassies of France, the United States, Rwanda, Uganda and Kenya in Kinshasa were attacked by local protesters. Demonstrators accused these countries of condoning Rwanda's support for the M23 rebels in the Democratic Republic of the Congo, which have now occupied the eastern provincial capital of Goma.
"All this is Rwanda's fault. Rwanda's actions are in collusion with France, Belgium, the United States and other countries. The Congolese people are tired. How many more times do we have to die?" The protesters claimed that the protest was aimed at asking the international community to put pressure on Rwanda to reveal its alleged involvement in the matter.
